cscie97.asn4.ecommerce.collection

Class ContentProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • cscie97.asn4.ecommerce.collection.Collectible
      • cscie97.asn4.ecommerce.collection.ContentProxy

  • public class ContentProxy
extends Collectible
    Wrapper class for Content objects that may be contained in Collections. Since all items that may be part of a Collection must be able to be easily iterated over, Content items must be wrapped so that they can inherit the same properties and be treated similarly by the CollectionIterator.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    David Killeffer <rayden7@gmail.com>
    See Also:
    Content, Collection, Collectible, DynamicCollection, StaticCollection

    • Constructor Detail

      • ContentProxy

        public ContentProxy(java.lang.String contentId)
        Class constructor. Given the passed contentId, looks up the associated Content item in the IProductAPI, and wraps the returned object so that the item inherits from Collectible and can be easily iterated over by CollectionIterator and contained in Collectibles.
        Parameters:
        contentId - the content ID of the associated Content item to wrap

      • ContentProxy

        public ContentProxy(Content contentItem)
        Class constructor. Given the passed Content item, wraps it around the ContentProxy so that the item inherits from Collectible and can be easily iterated over by CollectionIterator and contained in Collectibles.
        Parameters:
        contentItem - the content item to wrap
